# Next.js Frontend Rules

- Server Components by default; `'use client'` only for interactivity
- Data fetching: `apiServerFetch` in server components; TanStack Query in client islands
- UI from `@varnarc/ui`; permissions via `@varnarc/auth` `hasPermission()`
- Admin BFF routes under `apps/admin/src/app/api/admin/` proxy to NestJS API
- Loading, empty, and error states on all data pages
- Use semantic HTML; keyboard-accessible controls
- Security headers via `withSecurityHeaders()` in `next.config.ts`

Copy-paste prompt: `cursor/prompts/frontend.md` or `cursor/prompts/admin.md`
